"title": "7230: genealogies",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7230",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In Scripture, lists of the descendants or forebears of an individual, or a record of the names of particular groups of people.</p>\n<h2>Genealogies as records of ancestors and lines of descent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:1-Matt1:17\">MAT 1:1–1:17</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:23-Luke3:38\">LUK 3:23–3:38</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen10:1-Gen10:32\">GEN 10:1–10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:10-Gen11:32\">GEN 11:10–11:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen36:10-Gen36:43\">GEN 36:10–36:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr1:1-1Chr6:30\">1CH 1:1–6:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:35-1Chr9:44\">1CH 9:35–9:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:3\">HEB 7:3</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of genealogies</h2>\n<h3>Population lists</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:1\">1CH 9:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen46:8-Gen46:27\">GEN 46:8–46:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:3-1Chr9:22\">1CH 9:3–9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:16\">2CH 31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:1-Ezra2:67\">EZR 2:1–2:67</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:5-Neh7:69\">NEH 7:5–7:69</a></p>\n<h3>Heads of families</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:34\">1CH 9:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr8:1-1Chr8:28\">1CH 8:1–8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:7-1Chr9:9\">1CH 9:7–9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:31\">1CH 26:31</a></p>\n<h3>Men eligible for military service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr7:2\">1CH 7:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num26:1-Num26:62\">NUM 26:1–26:62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr7:4-1Chr7:11\">1CH 7:4–7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr7:30-1Chr7:40\">1CH 7:30–7:40</a></p>\n<h2>Some prophets may have been responsible for recording or maintaining genealogies</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:15\">2CH 12:15</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Christians are urged to avoid fruitless discussions concerning genealogies</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:9\">TIT 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3-1Tim1:4\">1TI 1:3–1:4</a></p>",
